'''2014年阿爾及利亞C-130力士型運輸機墜機事件'''是發生於2014年2月11日的一起航空事故。一架[[阿爾及利亞空軍|阿爾及利亞空軍]]所屬的[[C-130運輸機|C-130力士型運輸機]]墜毀在阿爾及利亞境內的[[烏姆布瓦吉省|烏姆布瓦吉省]]艾因喀查（Aïn Kercha）附近<ref name="BBC-One"/><ref>{{cite web|title=ASN Aircraft accident Lockheed C-130H-30 Hercules 7T-WHM Aïn Kercha|url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=20140211-0|publisher=Aviation Safety Network|accessdate=2014-02-11|archive-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224012144/http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=20140211-0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當時機上共有74名乘客及4名機組員，最終77人喪生，僅一人倖存<ref name="nyt-11/2"/><ref>{{cite news|title=At least 103 dead after military plane crashes in Algeria|url=http://voiceofrussia.com/news/2014_02_11/At-least-119-dead-after-military-plane-crashes-in-Algeria-7847/|accessdate=2014-02-11|publisher=[[俄羅斯之聲|俄羅斯之聲]]|date=2014-02-11|archive-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224012136/https://sputniknews.com/?utm_source=redirect_sputnik&utm_medium=redirect&utm_campaign=redirect%2Fnews%2F2014_02_11%2FAt-least-119-dead-after-military-plane-crashes-in-Algeria-7847%2F|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

初步報告顯示惡劣的天候可能是墜機的原因<ref>{{cite news|title=TV: Over 100 feared dead as military plane crashes in Algeria (update)|url=http://en.trend.az/regions/met/arabicr/2240748.html|accessdate=2014-02-11|publisher=Trend News Agency|date=2014-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223051953/http://en.trend.az/regions/met/arabicr/2240748.html|archive-date=2014-02-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="rt">{{cite news|title=Over 100 feared dead as military plane crashes in Algeria – local TV|url=http://rt.com/news/algeria-plane-crash-dead-542/|accessdate=2014-02-11|publisher=[[今日俄羅斯|今日俄羅斯]]|date=2014-02-11|archive-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224012140/https://www.rt.com/news/algeria-plane-crash-dead-542/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。目擊者則表示飛機墜毀前先削過了一座山<ref name="rt"/>。這也是阿爾及利亞繼2003年的[[阿爾及利亞航空6289號班機空難|阿爾及利亞航空6289號班機空難]]以來再度發生大型墜機事故<ref name="nyt-11/2"/>。

== 事故飛機 ==
事故飛機是編號7T-WHM的美製[[C-130運輸機|C-130力士型運輸機]]。製造商[[洛克希德·馬丁|洛克希德·馬丁]]證實曾於1981年至1990年間向阿爾及利亞售出C-130H運輸機。根據{{link-en|Flightglobal|Flightglobal}}，阿國共擁有十六架此型飛機<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2014/02/11/103-reportedly-dead-after-military-plane-crashes-in-algeria/|title="77 dead, 1 survivor in Algeria plane crash, official says"|publisher=foxnews.com.|date=2014-02-11|accessdate=2014-02-11|archive-date=2014-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140211161611/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2014/02/11/103-reportedly-dead-after-military-plane-crashes-in-algeria/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 天候狀況 ==
{{link-en|阿爾及利亞國防部|Military of Algeria}}表示惡劣氣候可能造成了此次災難發生<ref name="reuters">{{cite web|url =http://uk.reuters.com/article/2014/02/11/uk-algeria-crash-idUKBREA1A0YF20140211|title =Algerian military plane crashes into mountain, 77 killed|publisher =[[路透社|路透社]]|date =2014-02-11|accessdate =2014-02-11|archive-date =2014-02-22|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140222213835/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2014/02/11/uk-algeria-crash-idUKBREA1A0YF20140211|dead-url =no}}</ref>，當時飛機遭遇到[[暴風雪|暴風雪]]使得視野不佳<ref name="nyt-11/2">{{cite web| url =http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/12/world/africa/algerian-military-plane-crash.html| title =Military Plane Crash in Algeria Leaves Scores Dead| work =[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]| date =2014-0211| accessdate =2014-02-11| archive-date =2018-12-24| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20181224012142/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/12/world/africa/algerian-military-plane-crash.html| dead-url =no}}</ref>。

根據[[AccuWeather|AccuWeather]]，事故時飛機正在通過高海拔[[低氣壓|低氣壓]]區，天空交雜著雨雪。氣象學者Eric Leister補充：「在該區的數個地方出現超過30英哩的陣風伴隨雨雪」<ref name="nyt">{{cite web| url =http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/12/world/africa/algerian-military-plane-crash.html?_r=0| title =Dozens Said to Die in Algerian Military Plane Crash| work =[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]| date =2014-02-11| accessdate =2014-02-11| archive-date =2014-03-03| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140303042259/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/12/world/africa/algerian-military-plane-crash.html?_r=0| dead-url =no}}</ref>。

== 事故過程 ==
一架[[阿爾及利亞空軍|阿爾及利亞空軍]][[C-130運輸機|C-130力士型運輸機]]墜毀於[[烏姆布瓦吉省|烏姆布瓦吉省]]Aïn Kercha的Djebel Fertas山<ref name="BBC-One"/>，造成77人喪生，僅一人存活<ref name="nyt-11/2"/>。乘客名單包括軍人及軍人的家屬<ref name=BBC-One>{{cite news|title=Algerian army plane crashes - dozens dead, one survivor|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-26138101|accessdate=2014-0211|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=2014-02-11|archive-date=2014-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140211170310/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-26138101|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

